      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Ops Legend\n- **Green**: healthy or within target\n- **Amber**: warning, investigate trend\n- **Red**: breach or incident response required\n\n**Interpretation notes**\n- Cumulative totals are informational and use neutral coloring.\n- Ratio and health panels use threshold-based colors.\n- `Metrics Stale = 1` means scrape/data flow issue to triage first."
